he <LOCATION> Brooklyn </LOCATION> congregation. The Torah was flown to <LOCATION> New </LOCATION> <LOCATION> York </LOCATION> Tuesday in time for the sundown start of Yom Kippur, the most solemn holiday on the Jewish calendar.
