<HEAD>Judge Sets Hearing on Whether Former CIA Agent Can Be Indicted
Again</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By JAMES ROWLEY</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
